[A good perspective on the future living with COVID, questioning whether it will follow the pattern of influenza needing annual updates of the vaccine composition, or not. But it is increasingly clear the pandemic will not end this year, and different countries will reopen in different stages. The concern for emergence of new zoonotic viruses before the pandemic ends is real and should encourage countries to be vigilant. - Mod.LK]

